# Installer binaries — served as static files on the web host, NOT tracked in git.
# The per-version directories under public_html/4.NN/ live on the production
# server only; git versions the website source, not the download archive.
# Covers plain installers plus encrypted (.exe.gpg) and archived (.7z/.zip) builds.
*.exe
*.gpg
*.7z
*.zip

# LookingGlass runtime state (per-IP SQLite rate-limit DB)
LookingGlass/ratelimit.db

# Installer build toolchain — abandoned NSIS direction, not website content.
# (Lives in public_html/ on the server but is not part of the site.)
NSIS/
build/
*.nsi
make_setup_file.bat

# Callsign database — uploaded separately via the program-repo (n4af/TR4W)
# release process, like the installers. The live copy stays on the web host.
TRMASTER.DTA
TRMASTER.ASC

# Secrets / information disclosure — must never be in a public repo.
# (Also remove these from the live server: they are world-readable at tr4w.net/)
info.php
serial+key.txt

# Editor / backup / test cruft
*.swp
*.bak
*~
.ftpquota
.DS_Store
.bakindex.php
index.html.10.14
index.html.20260602
tr.out
testupload.txt
